doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    title Welcome to KiranaWala
    style.
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #4CAF50;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #4CAF50;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #777;
      }
  body
      .header
      h1 Welcome to KiranaWala!
   .content
  p Hello #{firstName},
  p We're excited to have you on board as a valued KiranaWala partner!
  p Your account has been successfully created and you can now start managing your store inventory, orders, and deliveries through our platform.
  p Your Store ID is: **#{storeId}**
  p Please keep this ID safe. You'll need it for support and verification purposes.
  p Get started by exploring your dashboard:
  a.button(href=url) Go to Dashboard
  p If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team at support@kiranawala.com
  p Thank you for being an active part of setting up your store. Your involvement plays a key role in making KiranaWala better for everyone.
  p Happy selling!
  p The KiranaWala Team

    .footer
      p Â© #{new Date().getFullYear()} KiranaWala. All rights reserved.
      p If you didn't request this email, please ignore it.